Package: BigDataAlgorithms
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2017-06-29
Title: Bioconductor Algorithms for Big Data
Author: Aaron Lun <alun@wehi.edu.au>
Maintainer: Aaron Lun <alun@wehi.edu.au>
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
Imports: HDF5Array, DelayedArray, Matrix
Suggests: testthat, BiocStyle, knitr
biocViews: DataRepresentation, DataImport, Infrastructure 
Description: Provides common algorithms for large data sets stored as
    including Matrix, DelayedArray and HDF5Array objects. This includes
    nearest-neighbour discovery, randomized SVD and PCA.
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: yes
VignetteBuilder: knitr
